data.description: Located in DESIRABLE Foxfield Meadows, This 4 BEDROOM BEAUTY Flows FLAWLESSLY!! Featuring an OPEN FLOOR PLAN, the Kitchen Granite Compliments the Richness of the Espresso Cabinets While the LARGE Island and Deep Sink Completes your Kitchen Wish List! You’ll Be Impressed by the Spacious Rooms and The Primary Suite which Features a Walk-In Closet and Ensuite with an Oversized Shower, Soaking Tub, and Double Vanity! Oh, Did We Mention the BRAND NEW CARPET UPSTAIRS, the FRESHLY PAINTED UPSTAIRS & The FRESHLY PAINTED HALL TREE W/ BENCH?! The Huge 12x12 Deck Backs Up to an INCREDIBLE Green Space Allowing you to Make the Most of the EXTRA YARD SPACE!! CENTRAL to Shopping, Hospital, and Less than a 30 Min Drive to Portsmouth Naval Medical Center, and Portsmouth Shipyard! Walking/Jogging Trails Throughout and a Playground for the Kiddos! Sure...Go Ahead and Add Your Personal Touch! This 6 Yr YOUNG Baby Will Do You PROUD! Schedule Your Appointment to See NOW!!
